64 Rūpāvacaraduka, Kusalattika
Rūpāvacaraduka, Kusalattika
73.
199Rūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Narūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
200Narūpāvacaraṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ. (Abyākatamūlaṃ dve paccayavasena.)
